    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-beginning-with-re" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are the best Scrabble words beginning with RE?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "REZONE (15 pts), REJUDGE (16 pts), and REEQUIP (18 pts) are among the highest-scoring RE- words. Common strong plays include REWORK (13 pts), REVAMP (13 pts), and REFLEX (16 pts). The RE- prefix is especially valuable because R and E are the two most common tiles in the bag." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do I front-hook RE onto existing Scrabble words?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Front-hooking with RE means adding RE- to a word already played. If PLAY is on the board, extend it to REPLAY. If LOAD is there, make it RELOAD. You score the full new word plus crosswords. RE- hooks onto hundreds of verbs — MAKE, DO, FILL, FORM, BUILD, STOCK, CYCLE, and more." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is RE a good bingo stem in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "RE is one of the strongest bingo stems. At only 2 tiles (2 points), RE + any 5-letter verb = a 7-letter bingo worth 50+ bonus points. Common RE- bingos include RETRACE, REBUILD, RESTFUL, RECOUNT, and REVISED. Since R and E appear frequently, you'll hold this combination often." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Word Lists</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Beginning with RE — Repeat, Rebuild, and Re-Score in Scrabble</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-14">June 14, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>7 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔍</span> Solver</a> <a href="/activities/#quiz" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎯</span> Quiz</a> <a href="/activities/#anagram" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔀</span> Anagram</a> <a href="/activities/#rack" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎲</span> Rack</a> <a href="/activities/#wotd" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">📖</span> WOTD</a> <a href="/sixty-seconds/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span> 60s</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">
        RE- is the single most common prefix in the English language, and that frequency translates directly into Scrabble power. Meaning "again" or "back," it attaches to thousands of verbs to create valid plays. With R (1 pt) and E (1 pt) being the two most frequently drawn tiles in the game, you'll find yourself holding this prefix constantly — the question is how to exploit it for maximum points.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">High-Scoring RE- Words for Scrabble</h2>

      <p>These RE- words combine the common prefix with premium-value tiles to deliver strong scores. Many are 7-8 letters long, making them natural bingo candidates.</p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Length</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REEQUIP</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To equip again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">RECHECK</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To check again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REJUDGE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To judge again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REFLEX</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Involuntary response</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REZONE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To change zoning of</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REFIX</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To fix again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REWAX</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To apply wax again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REVAMP</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To renovate or improve</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REWORK</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To work on again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">RESTOCK</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To replenish supply</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REBOOK</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To book again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">REBUILD</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To construct again</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">RECOUNT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To count again; narrate</td></tr>
